  "description": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2014/02/27/game-makers-can-now-start-their-own-steam-sales/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/72b410fb73bfca688e7df4ba1e79821f/steam-developer-created-sales.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nValve <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Steam/\">Steam</a> 刚刚推出了一个将会受到游戏开发者和玩家欢迎的措施，就是最新的 Steamworks 中，游戏的开发者可以自行设定自己的游戏折扣和打折的时限有多长。就算他们加入了 Valve 平日所举办的一星期减价活动，也是可以自决价格。虽然目前不知道这个新措施会不会很容易就引起开发者们割喉式的竞争，只是，给开发者在定价上有更大的自由度，和给消费者有更低的价格的话，总是比没有好的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/26/game-makers-can-now-start-their-own-steam-sales/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/Steam/comments/1yy56p/steamwork_developers_now_can_self_discount_their/\">Reddit</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/28/game-makers-can-now-start-their-own-steam-sales/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20839454/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/28/game-makers-can-now-start-their-own-steam-sales/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
